snippet.textDisplay:
This is like fresh air to CSB music. Emon Chowdhury vai is superb. A gem of bd music. The whole song gave such a vibe which is kind of epic and yet soothing.. Kinda hard to explain. 
I would top this song in this season. Then nodir kul and finally darale duare... 
Other songs were just a single time enjoyer song. And it became quite monotonous and hard to bear to hear saxophone and trumpet solos in every song.
